title: [SOLVED]Macbook air, 820 00165, Fan High Speed
message:
What does Apple Diagnostics give you for error codes?

Do you have completely assembled the board into its casing? Otherwise it will indeed run at full speed because various sensors (like in the trackpad) won't be connected.
